  "consentAiBody": "Swasth uses third-party AI services (Google Gemini and DeepSeek) to generate personalised health recommendations. A summary of my health data (not raw readings) may be sent to these services. I can opt out at any time, and rule-based insights will be used instead.",
  "consentAccept": "I Accept",
