  "ppAi": "Swasth uses third-party AI services — Google Gemini and DeepSeek — to generate health recommendations. A summarised version of your data (averages and ranges, not individual readings) is sent to these services. You can opt out of AI processing at any time; rule-based insights will be used instead.",
